Run begins at 1:15 and ends at 52:51; final in-game time is 47:58.049 with 1 berry and 46 deaths; game version is 1.4.0.0.

This is my seventh Celeste speedrun attempt, and my first attempt which I recorded for submission. It is also my personal best, and my first ever sub-48 run.

I was really expecting to not even make sub-50 during the run, because I was making a lot of silly mistakes. Just goes to show how much room for improvement I have!

This run improved my best segment times for three chapters:  
Forsaken City improves from 1:37.699 to 1:32.582  
Celestial Resort improves from 7:24.737 to 7:11.902  
The Summit improves from 13:42.919 to 13:39.485  
My best of segments time improves from 46:20.435 to 45:59.049.
